{"word":"G616 - ἀποκυέω - apokyéō - ap-ok-oo-eh'-o - Beget","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκυέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apokyéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok-oo-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beget</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரப்பி, ஜநிப்பி"},{"paragraph":"to bring forth from the womb, give birth to, to produce"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2949 - κῦμα - kŷma - koo'-mah/2949\">G2949</a>; to <i>breed forth</i>, that is, (by transformation) to <i>generate</i> (figuratively): - beget, bring forth.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}